  "ω ≈ 4.08 rad/s": "",
  "ω ≈ 1.83 rad/s": "",
  "Normal force provides centripetal force: N = mω²r. Friction must support weight: μ_s N = mg. μ_s mω²r = mg. ω = sqrt(g/(μ_s r)) = sqrt(10/(0.4×3)) = sqrt(8.33) ≈ 2.89 rad/s.": "",
